high_descs: Go to the right and then left and then turn right to face the black table with the plant.
Pick the watch up from the table.
Turn around and cross the room and then turn to the right to face the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a watch and turn a lamp on.

high_descs: Walk to the dresser table on your right.
Grab the watch from the table.
Walk around the sofa and go to the lamp behind the loveseat.
anns.task_desc: Look at a watch under a lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk past the right side of the couch and turn right to face the black table.
Pick up the watch on the black table.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the lamp in the corner.
Turn on the lamp to examine the watch.
anns.task_desc: To examine a watch by lamp light.
